<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.5">
<l>māṉēy nōkki maṭavāḷai mārviṟ koṇṭāy mātavā</l>
<l>kūṉē citaiya vuṇṭaivi ṉiṟatti ṟeṟittāy kōvintā</l>
<l>vāṉār cōti maṇivaṇṇā matucū tānī yaruḷāyuṉ</l>
<l>ṟēṉē malarun tiruppātañ cēru māṟu viṉaiyēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who take to [your] chest the yourful girl with deer-like glances, o Mātava,</l>
<l>you who who broke the bow quality of the ball so that [its] humps were spoiled, o Govinda,</l>
<l>light of the celestials, sapphire-coloured one, Madhusūdana, you grace</l>
<l>me of [bad] karma with a way to join your honey-blossoming sacred feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
